{"tid":1545572,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"兔子不親人的誤會已被棄養......","createTime":"2019-09-06T03:18:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T03:20:14.000Z","uid":197098,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c1b8ed4bee2cbf0954ea1969bbac6bce2a688174","tid":1545572,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:18:15.000Z","msg":"無視主人的誤會而被棄養：其實兔子側面看某東西就代表正面看某東西。牠們正前方和下方是盲點，除了這兩個盲點外，牠們幾乎可以看到360度。(所以有時食物在牠下巴下面睇唔到) <ins>你在他後面也會看到你</ins>。兔子只有向著前方大約30度範圍，才可以有立體影像。所以佢地唔係無視你，你是在他們視線範圍之內。牠們的脊椎就像軟骨那麼脆弱。另外也有遠視。<br />\n<br />\n兔子🐰是親人的群體性動物，但身體語言與其他動物不同，要做些研究才理解。(推介最底的3個網站)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">親人的動物：</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Maovq8Vz1LM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMaovq8Vz1LM&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H3jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=2fdfcd29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Maovq8Vz1LM</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pyL0yEs-ka8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpyL0yEs-ka8&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H3jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=705338ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pyL0yEs-ka8</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">兔子的行為解釋網站：</span><br />\n<br />\n香港兔協:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/knowledge8_ch.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2Fknowledge8_ch.php&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H3jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=fa84200d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/knowledge8_ch.php</a><br />\n<br />\n美國兔協 House Rabbit Society (教育網站):&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rabbit.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H3jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=f72aa479\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbit.org</a><br />\n<br />\n詳盡身體語言解釋(喜怒哀樂):&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rabbitspeak.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbitspeak.com&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H3jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=2f791ac0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbitspeak.com</a>"},{"pid":"f935caa5c15c37d47c1b2c5b553b4340299f1a66","tid":1545572,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:18:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"845a1153e1b85c14c518f77c722d672b4c0a5fa7","tid":1545572,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:19:07.000Z","msg":"907 機場攻略正式出爐，唔使再驚大逃走！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544251</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suRLDoM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuRLDoM.png&h=b3f794e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H3jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=7f1b088b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"fb54757b6689e0e0d9811eb12a793dce9f161217","tid":1545572,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:19:25.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd2634a6d23c3b2f4d1aa35cec35f3f86f3f0756","tid":1545572,"uid":649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:20:14.000Z","msg":"明明好痴人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}